-- Copyright 2002-2005.  Adobe Systems, Incorporated.  All rights reserved.-- This script shows how to crop the frontmost documenttell application "Adobe Photoshop CS2"	make new document with properties {width:2 as inches, height:2 as inches}		-- bounds are the region that you want to crop.	-- height and width are the dimensions of the resulting image	crop current document bounds {0.5 as inches, 0.5 as inches, 0.75 as inches, 0.75 as inches} Â		angle 45 width 1 as inches height 1 as inchesend tell